title: The TRUTH About Fantasy QBs: Part 2 + Dynasty Mailbag - Fantasy Football Podcast for 1/20
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive back into the TRUTH about fantasy quarterbacks! A fantasy football deep dive into the 2021 season for Russell Wilson, Lamar Jackson, Kirk Cousins, and others! Plus, a few dynasty trade questions answered in the Mailbag! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for January 20th, 2022.
  
 (04:30) - Quick Question: Most Surprising Teams
 (12:25) - The TRUTH About Fantasy QBs: Part Two
 (13:50) - Kirk Cousins
 (17:05) - Ryan Tannehill
 (19:55) - Derek Carr
 (22:20) - Carson Wentz
 (28:10) - Lamar Jackson
 (35:55) - Russell Wilson
 (41:25) - Mac Jones
 (46:00) - Dynasty Mailbag
